      "title": "Maskeliya has no petrol in nine days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three-wheeler drivers in the Maskeliya area blocked the main road in front of the Maskeliya petrol station, claiming that the only petrol station in Maskeliya had not received petrol for nine days.",
        "The protesters blocked the Hatton-Maskeliya and Hatton Nortonbridge main roads, causing severe traffic congestion for several hours.",
        "He said that his livelihood has been completely ruined due to the lack of petrol."
      ],
